title: Cubs Fan Is in It for the Long Run
text:
Cubs Fan Is in It for the Long Run Bleacher Report 4 hrs ago Thomas Duffy This young Chicago Cubs fan went above and beyond with a crazy real haircut bearing the image of star pitcher Jake Arrieta this week. Endless props to that barber.
AdChoices A night after chucking a complete-game shutout against the Pittsburgh Pirates in the National League Wild Card Game, the 29-year-old caught wind of the ‘do:
Wow, that is pretty awesome. https://t.co/YJukNKYj8n
— Jake Arrieta (@JArrieta34) October 9, 2015 [Twitter, h/t BSO ]
